      <title>“잘 지내시죠?” 설 연휴 앞두고 이른 성묘</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2025/01/20/QCIBS7QGVJHOTMVD72W7KEE4JA/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2025/01/20/QCIBS7QGVJHOTMVD72W7KEE4JA/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
      <description/>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 16:19:11 +0000</pubDate>
